---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="Finance">
  <div class="page-wrapper">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-serif);font-size:2rem;margin-bottom:6px;">Finance</h2>
      <p style="color:var(--muted);font-size:.9rem;margin-bottom:28px;">Notes on investing, personal finance, and building wealth as a tech professional.</p>

      <div class="callout">
        <strong>Not financial advice.</strong> Everything here is personal opinion and for educational purposes only. Do your own research.
      </div>

      <p class="section-label">Topics I write about</p>
      <div class="resource-list">
        <div class="resource-item">
          <span class="resource-emoji">📦</span>
          <div>
            <h3>Index Fund Investing</h3>
            <p>Why I keep most of my portfolio in low-cost index funds and how I think about allocation.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="resource-item">
          <span class="resource-emoji">🏠</span>
          <div>
            <h3>Real Estate vs. Equities</h3>
            <p>Breaking down the tradeoffs for tech workers with high W-2 income.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="resource-item">
          <span class="resource-emoji">💸</span>
          <div>
            <h3>Tax Strategy for Engineers</h3>
            <p>Mega backdoor Roth, RSU planning, and tax levers worth knowing at big tech companies.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="resource-item">
          <span class="resource-emoji">🛠</span>
          <div>
            <h3>Finance Tooling</h3>
            <p>Apps and tools I use to track net worth, budget, and stay on top of the market.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>
